Description: We recently upgraded and now have some reports that display data but we cannot download the data. (File not found error).

Trying to go in to the report configuration we receive the following error.

Unable to log error to SA: Object doesnt support porperty or method 'LogJSMessage'.
What We've Learned Updated: some users cannot download reports
Next Steps Updated: set report grid to interactive
